## objectid-to-timestamp

objectId to timestamp, in `ms`.

### Install

```
npm i objectid-to-timestamp --save
```

### Usage

```
var objectIdToTimestamp = require('objectid-to-timestamp');
objectIdToTimestamp('563229dd1ee6030100644cbe');// 1446128093391
```

### Test

```
npm test
```
